{"tid":599490,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人結婚唔同父母講？","createTime":"2018-03-20T12:42:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T15:26:20.000Z","uid":71253,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bc4a6e7d53b14612c4b00b5fe24a5345f4daaabe","tid":599490,"uid":71253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T12:42:26.000Z","msg":"岩先家姐返黎話下個禮拜就同男朋友入紙<br />\n佢平時完全冇提過自己有男朋友<br />\n<br />\n問佢有冇同老豆老母講，佢話唔打算講，反正結左婚之後會繼續比家用，佢地知唔知都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身我諗住叫佢點都同老豆老母講下，介紹男朋友比佢地識<br />\n不過其實我地同父母關係好疏離<br />\n一齊住但同老豆一個月講唔夠十句野，同老母已經幾年冇講過野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n突然間一齊飲茶介紹佢男朋友又好奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人結婚唔會同父母講？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家過成點？"},{"pid":"9bbea72b49e8f277d1f3e6fc078f61e346e0994e","tid":599490,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T12:44:05.000Z","msg":"應該無"},{"pid":"d29939acf49d87f0c7c2c84774db5dc93a670935","tid":599490,"uid":106375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T12:47:47.000Z","msg":"除非反曬面唔係一定會講聲"},{"pid":"b67bf8a57257333cd275b572b10fde03201dd57b","tid":599490,"uid":71253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d29939acf49d87f0c7c2c84774db5dc93a670935","tid":599490,"uid":106375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T12:47:47.000Z","msg":"除非反曬面唔係一定會講聲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T12:49:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會一齊食飯介紹下？唔會好尷尬咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff380a07698f4bfdf1c6e13e2829072df9b9f62","tid":599490,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T12:51:04.000Z","msg":"你家姐好憎你老豆老母咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b4bfeb5b5447bbfef621757237131137205d29","tid":599490,"uid":71253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dff380a07698f4bfdf1c6e13e2829072df9b9f62","tid":599490,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T12:51:04.000Z","msg":"你家姐好憎你老豆老母咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T12:58:48.000Z","msg":"我諗佢好憎老母，因為老母係出面有男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老豆就應該冇乜野，係唔太熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"427cd888a97403112b4866932ed3ff62df166870","tid":599490,"uid":41009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T14:11:40.000Z","msg":"有fd一直係同女朋友同居<br />\n然後入紙註埋冊先同屋企講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d524204b463cd753a0cf66c1ec053441a17306c","tid":599490,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98b4bfeb5b5447bbfef621757237131137205d29","tid":599490,"uid":71253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dff380a07698f4bfdf1c6e13e2829072df9b9f62","tid":599490,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T12:51:04.000Z","msg":"你家姐好憎你老豆老母咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T12:58:48.000Z","msg":"我諗佢好憎老母，因為老母係出面有男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老豆就應該冇乜野，係唔太熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"